So Nantes, the city I live in, had a lot of snow and it's not that common here. Public transportation was closed this morning and is barely even running now. But me being me, I still walked to the gym to see if it was open at 5:50 this morning. It was but not importantly look at all these snowmen I got to say hello to on the way there! (Bonus frost picture.)
